SELECT FOLLOWEE FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 WHERE EXISTS(SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW F2 WHERE F2.FOLLOWER = F1.FOLLOWEE) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE

SELECT B.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, NUM FROM (SELECT FOLLOWEE,IFNULL(COUNT(FOLLOWER),0) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING IFNULL(COUNT(FOLLOWER),0)>=1) B JOIN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWER HAVING IFNULL(COUNT(FOLLOWEE),0)>=1) A ON B.FOLLOWEE=A.FOLLOWER ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT F1.FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER HAVING NUM >=1 ORDER BY FOLLOWER

SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) AND FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE ASC
SELECT F1.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 INNER JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWEE = F2.FOLLOWER GROUP BY FOLLOWER ORDER BY FOLLOWER

WITH FO1 AS (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWER IN (SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW)) SELECT FOLLOWEE FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FO1) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWER) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT DISTINCT A.FOLLOWER,COUNT( DISTINCT B.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWER = B.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY A.FOLLOWER ORDER BY A.FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY 1 HAVING 2 >=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT A.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT A.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A LEFT JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWEE = B.FOLLOWER WHERE B.FOLLOWER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY A.FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT A.FOLLOWER) >= 1 ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT A.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT B.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWER = B.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY FOLLOWER
SELECT E.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT E.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F INNER JOIN FOLLOW E ON F.FOLLOWER = E.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY E.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY E.FOLLOWEE
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW ) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY 1
SELECT F1.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F2.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER

WITH CTE1 AS ( SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWER HAVING COUNT(*) >= 1 ) SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM CTE1) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(*) >= 1 ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT F.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F WHERE F.FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY F.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY F.FOLLOWEE
SELECT DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER ASC

WITH USERS AS ( SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWEE AS USER_ID FROM FOLLOW UNION SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER AS USER_ID FROM FOLLOW), DRV AS ( SELECT USERS.USER_ID FROM USERS WHERE USERS.USER_ID IN (SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) AND USERS.USER_ID IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW)) SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER ,COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT USER_ID FROM DRV) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT A.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER,A.NUM FROM( SELECT FOLLOWEE,COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) >=1) A LEFT JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWEE = B.FOLLOWER GROUP BY A.FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(B.FOLLOWEE) >= 1
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY 1 HAVING FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) ORDER BY 1

WITH T1 AS(SELECT DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW F1 LEFT JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE WHERE F2.FOLLOWEE IS NOT NULL GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER), T2 AS (SELECT COUNT(*) AS NUM, FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE) SELECT T1.FOLLOWER, T2.NUM FROM T1 LEFT JOIN T2 ON T1.FOLLOWER = T2.FOLLOWEE
SELECT F1.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 LEFT JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE WHERE F2.FOLLOWER IS NOT NULL GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER ORDER BY 1
SELECT DISTINCT F.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, F.NUM FROM (SELECT FOLLOWEE, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE) F JOIN FOLLOW FOLL ON F.FOLLOWEE = FOLL.FOLLOWER WHERE F.NUM > 0 ORDER BY 1
SELECT A.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT B.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A INNER JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWER = B.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY A.FOLLOWER ORDER BY A.FOLLOWER ASC

SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER , COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW F1, FOLLOW F2 WHERE F1.FOLLOWEE = F2.FOLLOWER ) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT A.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT B.FOLLOWER) NUM FROM FOLLOW A INNER JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWER = B.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT B.FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT A.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A JOIN FOLLOW B ON A.FOLLOWEE = B.FOLLOWER GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT FOLLOWEE FOLLOWER , COUNT(*) NUM FROM FOLLOW O WHERE EXISTS ( SELECT X FROM FOLLOW I WHERE O.FOLLOWEE=I.FOLLOWER ) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER ,COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY 1
SELECT A.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(1) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW A INNER JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) B USING (FOLLOWEE) GROUP BY A.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWER ASC
SELECT DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F2.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER ASC

WITH FOLLOWS_ONE AS (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER AS USR FROM FOLLOW), FOLLOWED_ONE AS (SELECT FOLLOWEE AS USR, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE) SELECT F2.USR AS FOLLOWER, NUM FROM FOLLOWS_ONE F1 JOIN FOLLOWED_ONE F2 ON F1.USR = F2.USR ORDER BY FOLLOWER
WITH XRS AS ( SELECT FOLLOWER AS USERS FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F JOIN XRS X ON X.USERS = F.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1
SELECT F1.FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 JOIN FOLLOW F2 WHERE F1.FOLLOWEE=F2.FOLLOWER GROUP BY FOLLOWER
SELECT DISTINCT F1.FOLLOWER, F2.NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 INNER JOIN (SELECT FOLLOWEE, COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE)F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER ASC
SELECT F1.FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT F2.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW AS F1 INNER JOIN FOLLOW AS F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW F1 WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE

SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) AND FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE

WITH FOLLOWING AS ( SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWER HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWEE)>=1 ), FOLLOWED AS ( SELECT FOLLOWEE, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER)>=1 ) SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, NUM FROM FOLLOWED WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT * FROM FOLLOWING) ORDER BY FOLLOWEE

WITH T1 AS (SELECT * FROM FOLLOW A WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM FOLLOW B WHERE A.FOLLOWEE=B.FOLLOWER)), T2 AS (SELECT * FROM T1 WHERE FOLLOWEE!=FOLLOWER) , T3 AS (SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM T2 GROUP BY FOLLOWEE) SELECT * FROM T3 ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER , COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW)) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWER

SELECT DISTINCT LVL2 AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT LVL3) AS NUM FROM ( SELECT F1.FOLLOWEE AS LVL1, F2.FOLLOWEE AS LVL2, F2.FOLLOWER AS LVL3 FROM FOLLOW F1 LEFT JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE UNION SELECT F1.FOLLOWEE AS LVL1, F2.FOLLOWEE AS LVL2, F2.FOLLOWER AS LVL3 FROM FOLLOW F1 RIGHT JOIN FOLLOW F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE ) TAB WHERE LVL1 IS NOT NULL AND LVL2 IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1 HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LVL3) >=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER , COUNT(*) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT A.FOLLOWEE FROM( SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) A JOIN( SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) B ON A.FOLLOWEE = B.FOLLOWER) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE

WITH CTE AS ( SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWEE AS FT FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) ) SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER ,COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FT FROM CTE) ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT R.FOLLOWER AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(DISTINCT E.FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW R INNER JOIN FOLLOW E ON R.FOLLOWER = E.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY FOLLOWER
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE HAVING COUNT(FOLLOWER)>=1 ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
WITH FOLLOWS AS ( SELECT FOLLOWEE, COUNT(DISTINCT FOLLOWER) NUM FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY 1 ) SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWER, NUM FROM FOLLOW, FOLLOWS WHERE FOLLOWER = FOLLOWS.FOLLOWEE ORDER BY 1

SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWER) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT FOLLOWEE AS USERS FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN (SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW) UNION SELECT FOLLOWER AS USERS FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWER IN (SELECT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW) ) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY FOLLOWEE
SELECT FOLLOWEE AS FOLLOWER, COUNT(FOLLOWEE) AS NUM FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWEE IN ( SELECT FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW WHERE FOLLOWER IN (SELECT DISTINCT FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW)) GROUP BY FOLLOWEE ORDER BY 1

WITH CTE_FOLLOWEE AS( SELECT FOLLOWEE, COUNT(*) AS COUNT_FOLLOWEE FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWEE), CTE_FOLLOWER AS ( SELECT FOLLOWER, COUNT(*) AS COUNT_FOLLOWER FROM FOLLOW GROUP BY FOLLOWER) SELECT F1.FOLLOWER, COUNT_FOLLOWEE AS NUM FROM CTE_FOLLOWER F1 INNER JOIN CTE_FOLLOWEE F2 ON F1.FOLLOWER = F2.FOLLOWEE GROUP BY F1.FOLLOWER ORDER BY F1.FOLLOWER
